Metadata.Title: Death of a Unicorn
Metadata.Description: After the wealthy family of Alexa Carlisle killed a unicorn the local fae community made a contract to kill the rest of the family. There apears to have been some infighting withing the family but it is of no matter a quick job must be done as the portal to return home will not be open long.The Contractors are willing to pay more for a poetic kill with a unicorn horn as an homage to the poor slain creature.  Make the Whole family go missing with no one the wiser before you leave.
